:<font size="15">לחי</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
לחי /  lechîy / lekh-ee'

===Etymology===
From an unused root meaning to be soft; 

===Noun===
'''לחי'''

# The cheek (from its fleshiness); hence the jaw bone: - cheek (bone), jaw (bone).

